[thinking] **Evaluating vintage dependencies**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm thinking about whether to add vintage support to the tck override. The existing build doesn't specify vintage but might be affected by a global plugin using version 5.9.2. If there's a Gradle conflict due to the same module, I wonder if adding the direct vintage version 6 will help. It seems like the JUnit Jupiter addition might not pull in vintage support directly, but existing tests already have it. So, adding `testRuntimeOnly` for JUnit Vintage seems reasonable for compatibility. I need to think this through a bit more!
